{"title":"fix: correct Deployment selector.matchLabels for vigil-app","body":"Root cause: Deployment manifest has mismatched selector and template labels: spec.selector.matchLabels.app is 'vigil-app-typo' but spec.template.metadata.labels.app is 'vigil-app', causing Kubernetes to reject the Deployment as invalid.

Evidence: Deployment.apps "vigil-app" is invalid: [spec.template.metadata.labels: Invalid value: {"app":"vigil-app"}: `selector` does not match template `labels`, spec.selector: Invalid value: {"matchLabels":{"app":"vigil-app-typo"}}: field is immutable]

This PR fixes the selector to match the template labels (both set to 'vigil-app')."}
